++++++++
Scrubber
++++++++

Scrubber is sort of like FormEncode_, but without all the metaclass and
introspection jazz.

Scrubber aims at handling those annoying corner cases really well.  On
the down side, you have to write more code, because not much happpens
through magic.

.. _FormEncode: http://formencode.org

.. vim: set syntax=rst:

